# Essential Features (When Applicable)

## Deep Linking
- Handle URL schemes and universal links
- Test deep linking thoroughly

## Notifications
- Handle permissions properly
- Process in foreground and background

## Background Tasks
- Use background task APIs correctly
- Respect system resource limits

## Localization
- Use NSLocalizedString for user-facing text
- Handle locale-specific formatting
- Test with different language settings

## Logging
- Use appropriate logging levels
- Avoid logging sensitive information
- Implement crash reporting
